            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]<strong> </span>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Roughly chop the <strong>Fable pulled mushrooms</strong> and add to the <strong>salt & pepper coating </strong>and give everything a good mix up until evenly coated</p><p>Once the pan is hot, shake off the excess cornflour and add the <strong>coated Fable mushrooms</strong>, then cook for 8-10 min, stirring occasionally, or until browned and crispy all over</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
